    {
      "title": "Replication data and code for: Citizen science in Ethiopia contests prevailing assumptions in formal seed systems concerning men and women smallholders’ preferences for crop varieties and traits, revealing their latent demand for diversity"
    }
  ],
  "publisher": "Zenodo",
